Comple- tion of the Planetary Christos Realignment will create a natural “D-12 Planetary Maharic Seal” in Earth’s Templar Complex Star Gates, Ley Lines and V ortices. A natural Planetary Maharic Seal will return the po- tentials of Immortal Life, Star Gate travel and Self-Directed Ascension to the Angelic Human Races of Earth, while protecting Earth and human- ity from any further Fallen Angelic infiltration. • The last SAC occurred on Earth in 208,216 BC during the First Evolution- ary Round of the Palaidia Urtite-Cloister Race 12-Tribes. In our present Time Continuum, the Palaidia Races were invaded by Fallen An- gelic Drakonian Races from Orion and were unable to successfully com- plete their intended Divine Commission. Earth entered pole shift in 208,216 BC, the Palaidia Empires were destroyed and survivors were re- settled to begin the Second Evolutionary Round of the Cycle of the Rounds. • Earth’s Planetary Shields have encountered progressively more misalign- ment and corruption since the failed 208,216 BC SAC.
